{"word":"δυνατός","slug":"δυνατός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δυνατός, ή, όν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δύναμαι\">δύναμαι</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘having power/competence’, mostly of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><i>competent, able, powerful</i> <a href='B:510 7:22'>Ac 7:22</a>; <a href='B:520 4:21'>Ro 4:21</a>; <a href='B:530 1:26'>1 Cor 1:26</a>; <a href='B:540 12:10'>2 Cor 12:10</a>; <a href='B:620 1:12'>2 Ti 1:12</a>; <a href='B:630 1:9'>Tit 1:9</a>; <a href='B:650 11:19'>Hb 11:19</a>; <a href='B:660 3:2'>Js 3:2</a>;</b> of things <b><a href='B:540 10:4'>2 Cor 10:4</a>.—</b>τὸ δ. of God <i>competence, power, ability</i> <b><a href='B:520 9:22'>Ro 9:22</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘capable of being realized’, <b><i>possible, realizable</i> <a href='B:470 19:26'>Mt 19:26</a>; <a href='B:480 9:23'>Mk 9:23</a>; <a href='B:490 18:27'>Lk 18:27</a>; <a href='B:510 2:24'>Ac 2:24</a>.—</b> <i><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰ\">εἰ</a></i> δ. <i>if possible</i> <b><a href='B:470 24:24'>Mt 24:24</a>; <a href='B:480 14:35'>Mk 14:35</a>; <a href='B:490 14:31'>Lk 14:31</a>; <a href='B:520 12:18'>Ro 12:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δυνατέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δύνῃ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}